  • Method Details

    • forKey

      static DialogLike forKey(RegistryKey<Dialog> key)

      Creates a new adventure DialogLike for the dialog at the given key.

      Useful for sending a dialog which has been pre-sent to the client in the Dialog registry.

      Parameters:
      key - the key of the dialog (must be registered)
      Returns:
      a new DialogLike for the dialog at the given key
